modName: Daenerys Targaryen aka Emilia Clarke personal preset
descriptionHtml:
My personal presets for Daenerys Targaryen.

After spending hours looking for a satistfying Dany I decided to create my own one. If you want her as a follower use "Familar faces". Feel free to add details I did not see ( I am lightly blind-color so I don't see every shades of colors).

Enjoy and send me your best pictures in a Khaleesi situation.

P.S: I did not customized it myself entirely I used J3rryW3st preset.

To J3rryW3st and of course Emilia Clarke for her face :)
author: Abdel938
